<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-04-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-04-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="403" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d403">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/831.</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-04-11">
                                    <hi rend="italic">April 11, 1913</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The Senate elected Bordas yesterday for the third time. Today the House
                            rejected him, 15 to 9, and later voted Jiménez, 8; Vásquez, 8;
                            Velásquez, 5.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Curtis</hi>.</signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
